function sysCall_init() corout=coroutine.create(coroutineMain) simRemoteApi.start(19999) end
function sysCall_actuation() if coroutine.status(corout)~='dead' then local ok,errorMsg=coroutine.resume(corout) if errorMsg then error(debug.traceback(corout,errorMsg),2) end end end
function coroutineMain() motorHandles={-1,-1,-1,-1}
motorHandles[1]=sim.getObjectHandle('leftFrontJoint') motorHandles[2]=sim.getObjectHandle('rightFrontJoint') motorHandles[3]=sim.getObjectHandle('leftRearJoint') motorHandles[4]=sim.getObjectHandle('rightRearJoint')
end
